room_title: Escape room "Kingdom of Cats" by Omescape in San Jose
room_address: 625 Wool Creek Drive, Suite E, San Jose, CA 95112
room_description: Austin Schrodinger rules the Kingdom of Cats. Every year, he holds a championship tournament to crown the wisest cat in the kingdom. Unexpectedly, you, as a human, accidentally join the championship and the battlefield. According to the law of the land, your entrance to the battlefield requires you to complete the tournament or be imprisoned here forever. Now, you have to accept the challenge and solve puzzles and riddles in the tournament.
